name: NWParameters.ExpiredDNSBehavior
desc: Options for configuring how expired DNS answers should be used.

items.name: case systemDefault
items.desc: Let the system determine whether or not to allow expired DNS answers.

items.name: case allow
items.desc: Explicitly allow the use of expired DNS answers.

items.name: case prohibit
items.desc: Explicitly prohibit the use of expired DNS answers.

items.name: static func != (NWParameters.ExpiredDNSBehavior, NWParameters.ExpiredDNSBehavior) -> Bool
items.desc: Returns a Boolean value indicating whether two values are not equal.
